About this item

  • ✪【Full RGB Backlight】Full RGB backlit, 6 themed lighting effects, 16.8 million colors adjustable. multiple backlit mode ( Aurora, Ripple, Music, Rainbow , Waves, Gradient, Windmill, Spectrum and single light), no drivers needed. The overall shape of the pudding keycap is like a pudding divided into two layers, one layer is solid color and the other layer is translucent. This can make the RGB play the most eye-catching lighting effect.
  • ✪【5000W Gateron Optical Switch】Yellow Exclusive V2 / Green / Red / Brown / Blue Optical switch is available. Gateron optical switches can be hot swapped at wish and full keyboard is hot swappable, plug and change, switch DIY. Hot swap keyboard do not recquire you to solder / desolder switches. (Hot Swappable with Optical switches only)
  • ✪【PBT Double-shot Pudding Keycaps】Different from ABS keycaps, these PBT keycaps are made of PBT Double-shot crafts and resistant to wear, friction, and solvents. So the keycaps patterns not easy to wear and excellent to touch. The durable and amazing touch feeling will definitlly your best companion!
  • ✪【Macro recording & Large On-board Memory】 Record macros through the software, customize advanced features, personnalize function keys. Full Anti Ghosting Mode (NKRO). All buttons are programmable, built-in large-capacity on-board memory, can remember the last light effect setting.
  • ✪【Compatibility with Mac and Windows】Compatible with Mac OS, Windows 10/ Win 8/ Win 7/ Win Vista/ Windows XP/ Android and Linux, the Keyboard comes with a 1.5m/59 inches USB Type-C 3.1cable. The keyboard is adapted for all environnement, Home & Office use, a Plug & Play small form factor keyboard for tiny spaces.

We want you to know: This is a product from the US and may differ from similar products sold locally. Please carefully review the labelling and other product information to determine if this product is appropriate for you. A power plug adapter may be required to fit UAE sockets.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
